Package com.google.android.droiddriver

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DroidDriver
    The entry interface for using droiddriver.
    Poller
    Interface for polling mechanism.
    Poller.ConditionChecker<T>
    Used by Poller to check conditions.
    Poller.ListenerRemover
    Interface for removing a listener.
    Poller.PollingListener
    Interface for a callback to be invoked when Poller.pollFor(com.google.android.droiddriver.DroidDriver, com.google.android.droiddriver.finders.Finder, com.google.android.droiddriver.Poller.ConditionChecker<T>) polls.
    Poller.TimeoutListener
    Interface for a callback to be invoked when Poller.pollFor(com.google.android.droiddriver.DroidDriver, com.google.android.droiddriver.finders.Finder, com.google.android.droiddriver.Poller.ConditionChecker<T>) times out.
    UiDevice
    Interface for device-wide interaction.
    UiElement
    Represents an UI element within an Android App.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    Poller.UnsatisfiedConditionException
    Thrown to indicate condition not met.
